data.description: Welcome to your new sanctuary nestled on a spacious corner lot! This charming one-story brick home offers many features that will make every day feel like a retreat. Step inside to discover vaulted ceilings & beautiful fireplace with brick hearth. With a dedicated study, formal living room, & formal dining room, there's no shortage of flexible spaces to meet all your needs, whether you're working from home or hosting guests. The kitchen features an island with electric cooktop, double ovens, & abundant cabinet & counter space. The primary suite boasts tray ceilings, fireplace, dual sinks, garden tub, & separate shower. All secondary bedrooms are generously sized & come with walk-in closets. Step outside to your very own private paradise. A beautiful pool & large covered patio provide the perfect spot for relaxation. Enjoy the utmost privacy in your outdoor haven. Contact us today to schedule a viewing!
